      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why i'm typing this. everything just feels... heavy. like i've spent years building this entire life around my research and now it's all just gone. the funding, the lab results, the future i thought i had. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting. i'm just so tired of existing like this.",
